{"tid":205220,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"馬係唔係私人寵物","createTime":"2017-04-17T15:28:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T02:15:13.000Z","uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"62d6023709a45825c726851262b00e0c4b05d61f","tid":205220,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T15:28:52.000Z","msg":"點解馬會有權將佢人道毀滅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n斷左隻手就要死 點解咁對佢喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以退投姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f468056baee4fd9428fed39e1255393f2ee6fca1","tid":205220,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T15:35:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a288cef0be2ad8152e1e677365afc394db90a992","tid":205220,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T15:39:59.000Z","msg":"因為救黎都無用 無得再跑 馬有得比人人道毀滅 <br />\n運動員斷手斷腳 坐輪椅 人生已完但無得安樂死<br />\n你永遠都唔會知到運動員無得再比賽嘅痛苦 因為殘疾令佢由天堂跌落地獄<br />\n馬都一樣 佢無得再跑 係人嘅角度黎睇 雖然唔會明馬嘅諗法 但可能人道毀滅 係唯一一種對佢好嘅做法"},{"pid":"f83926090ab5873bf30ad7829e29d72127761345","tid":205220,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T15:56:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為救黎都無用 無得再跑 馬有得比人人道毀滅 <br />\n運動員斷手斷腳 坐輪椅 人生已完但無得安樂死<br />\n你永遠都唔會知到運動員無得再比賽嘅痛苦 因為殘疾令佢由天堂跌落地獄<br />\n馬都一樣 佢無得再跑 係人嘅角度黎睇 雖然唔會明馬嘅諗法 但可能人道毀滅 係唯一一種對佢好嘅做法</blockquote><br />\n馬唔跑場咪退休 唔洗死<br />\n可能佢都唔想跑 想慢慢生活<br />\n好殘忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我以為隻狗狗有隻手都唔好 但佢都活得開心<br />\n其他狗都好錫佢同就佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dc0cc4bf25491071269df9e6e1afc44ec99c459","tid":205220,"uid":14819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T16:23:27.000Z","msg":"咪就係<br />\n骨折啫 醫都唔醫就殺左佢<br />\n仲話自己係慈善機構<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dcd12ada2bc9b0f0295c4fb7173ded381d4f7e6","tid":205220,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T17:11:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咪就係<br />\n骨折啫 醫都唔醫就殺左佢<br />\n仲話自己係慈善機構<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 洗唔洗殺<br />\n根本就唔人道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好慘 馬會諗自己做錯所以被殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f985a7e96f5ede31830ceb9b31cbe83120c27978","tid":205220,"uid":36049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T17:13:09.000Z","msg":"狗會serve 既係有錢佬<br />\n你班賤民佢地鬼理你"},{"pid":"76d58ad45193409b8045a22d298b19cb88c5021d","tid":205220,"uid":29724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T17:13:57.000Z","msg":"好似係做完手術隻馬其實條命都唔得長，做完手術都係企唔得返起身，所以無謂要隻馬再受苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6acf5f79afa7df8de6658dae5c6bcafe760fa51","tid":205220,"uid":40588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T17:15:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咪就係<br />\n骨折啫 醫都唔醫就殺左佢<br />\n仲話自己係慈善機構<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nGOOGLE下先啦"},{"pid":"a3afbe7e004b3f93a374555ee8d7ff2e6595e692","tid":205220,"uid":78614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T17:21:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c2614f3a4e0b2ba4ed1bef90bd0c95ea6387f57","tid":205220,"uid":78614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T17:22:26.000Z","msg":"有併發症都係會死 仲辛苦"},{"pid":"e5c464565e68d8c99e6bb7276701491418081b2f","tid":205220,"uid":54658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T17:26:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20150414/19111344\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20150414%2F19111344&d=hYhEKVoQeS8%2B2u2S5aPGGW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=a94dea79\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20150414%2F19111344&h=b77ec6fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20150414/19111344</a><br />\n比大家參考下 到底點解要人道毀滅<br />\n錢當然係一個因素 但係好老實講 唔係個個都咁冷血 <br />\n隻馬斷左腳 要佢繼續生存好殘忍<br />\n又痛又唔郁得 對隻馬嚟講先係最慘<br />\n始終馬鐘意跑 鐘意活動<br />\n比佢安樂咁走 唔洗受苦可能係好事<br />\n當然無人知隻馬諗咩 <br />\n但我相信馬主同獸醫嘅出發點都係想隻馬好 安安樂樂咁走 唔好受咁多苦<br />\n發生呢啲事我相信無人想 <br />\n馬主對馬無感情就唔會選擇養馬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62cf27a22bc201170017879687b5cc4e7119b000","tid":205220,"uid":21488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T17:32:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20150414/19111344\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20150414%2F19111344&d=hYhEKVoQeS8%2B2u2S5aPGGW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=a94dea79\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20150414%2F19111344&h=b77ec6fd\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20150414/19111344</a><br />\n比大家參考下 到底點解要人道毀滅<br />\n錢當然係一個因素 但係好老實講 唔係個個都咁冷血 <br />\n隻馬斷左腳 要佢繼續生存好殘忍<br />\n又痛又唔郁得 對隻馬嚟講先係最慘<br />\n始終馬鐘意跑 鐘意活動<br />\n比佢安樂咁走 唔洗受苦可能係好事<br />\n當然無人知隻馬諗咩 <br />\n但我相信馬主同獸醫嘅出發點都係想隻馬好 安安樂樂咁走 唔好受咁多苦<br />\n發生呢啲事我相信無人想 <br />\n馬主對馬無感情就唔會選擇養馬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但最後個句並不認同<br />\n香港馬主大多數都仆街<br />\n隻馬有事都要抖番排再跑 唔比佢退役<br />\n純粹只係一個賺錢工具"},{"pid":"d203570e8857686393b61900ac0a8aa7ae7fa659","tid":205220,"uid":2151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T17:33:52.000Z","msg":"上面班友骨折都講得出 睇新聞片啦 <br />\n隻馬斷到定左起度唔識郁隻右前蹄斷到fing下fing下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d94baaecd7da89e6c424b5e07d7bb077a8c6bf4f","tid":205220,"uid":29880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T17:34:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解馬會有權將佢人道毀滅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n斷左隻手就要死 點解咁對佢喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以退投姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你俾錢養?"},{"pid":"0fe54fcf585bcc4231d8bd80ba08d219661ce7ce","tid":205220,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T17:36:01.000Z","msg":"如果個馬主斷腳又唔見拎去人道毀滅"},{"pid":"2593eba8c01475c1111ff75d1cdfc5dd921c32b8","tid":205220,"uid":40588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T22:57:41.000Z","msg":"隔離post<br />\n<br />\n美國有馬匹網站表示，除了龐大醫藥費，斷腳馬治好也沒法再參賽外，對斷腳馬匹進行人道毀滅，主要是考慮到馬匹本身。一般馬有約一千磅體重，由幼細的四肢支撐，其中一隻腳骨折的話，其餘三隻的負荷便會增加，容易造成馬足板層炎、膿腫等問題，令馬匹傷上加傷。<br />\n<br />\n另外，馬匹四肢膝蓋以下的地方沒有肌肉，只要一受傷，血流量便會受影響；加上骨頭刺穿皮膚的地方接觸到泥巴和草，容易感染細菌，均會增加出現併發症的風險。但偏偏馬是天性好動，病情稍為好轉，就會亂動亂跑，再次弄傷。病情反覆，令馬匹承受極大痛楚，倒不如人道毀滅，長痛不如短痛。"},{"pid":"d22922e8bcd1d4cea09fbfc391057288e50eeef3","tid":205220,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T01:12:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上面班友骨折都講得出 睇新聞片啦 <br />\n隻馬斷到定左起度唔識郁隻右前蹄斷到fing下fing下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n新聞都係講骨折"},{"pid":"3f70d4da4db543d4cc2decd7c14199d18548c022","tid":205220,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T01:12:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>隔離post<br />\n<br />\n美國有馬匹網站表示，除了龐大醫藥費，斷腳馬治好也沒法再參賽外，對斷腳馬匹進行人道毀滅，主要是考慮到馬匹本身。一般馬有約一千磅體重，由幼細的四肢支撐，其中一隻腳骨折的話，其餘三隻的負荷便會增加，容易造成馬足板層炎、膿腫等問題，令馬匹傷上加傷。<br />\n<br />\n另外，馬匹四肢膝蓋以下的地方沒有肌肉，只要一受傷，血流量便會受影響；加上骨頭刺穿皮膚的地方接觸到泥巴和草，容易感染細菌，均會增加出現併發症的風險。但偏偏馬是天性好動，病情稍為好轉，就會亂動亂跑，再次弄傷。病情反覆，令馬匹承受極大痛楚，倒不如人道毀滅，長痛不如短痛。</blockquote><br />\n儀肢得唔得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dca6eb9f1da430d915a95a07e4fff84784b7f917","tid":205220,"uid":34503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T01:21:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>隔離post<br />\n<br />\n美國有馬匹網站表示，除了龐大醫藥費，斷腳馬治好也沒法再參賽外，對斷腳馬匹進行人道毀滅，主要是考慮到馬匹本身。一般馬有約一千磅體重，由幼細的四肢支撐，其中一隻腳骨折的話，其餘三隻的負荷便會增加，容易造成馬足板層炎、膿腫等問題，令馬匹傷上加傷。<br />\n<br />\n另外，馬匹四肢膝蓋以下的地方沒有肌肉，只要一受傷，血流量便會受影響；加上骨頭刺穿皮膚的地方接觸到泥巴和草，容易感染細菌，均會增加出現併發症的風險。但偏偏馬是天性好動，病情稍為好轉，就會亂動亂跑，再次弄傷。病情反覆，令馬匹承受極大痛楚，倒不如人道毀滅，長痛不如短痛。</blockquote><br />\n儀肢得唔得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係咪女人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9149976589eedea163012d2ad09bf6c3b645282","tid":205220,"uid":1065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T01:23:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://files.explosm.net/comics/Rob/horseyride.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffiles.explosm.net%2Fcomics%2FRob%2Fhorseyride.png&h=dce4555d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee2fa6eb694d560e51704a2d0694c3b7fc0b3608","tid":205220,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T01:25:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://files.explosm.net/comics/Rob/horseyride.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffiles.explosm.net%2Fcomics%2FRob%2Fhorseyride.png&h=dce4555d&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就係咁 你有冇問過佢想唔想做賽馬定係想自由生活"},{"pid":"3f6bceb5f8b36688098f472ba666917029ec9159","tid":205220,"uid":3581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor